- title "Home"

%section.left
  %section.posts_excerpt
    %header
      %h3 Recent posts
      = link_to "View all", posts_path
    - @posts.each do |post|
      %article
        %h4= link_to post.title, post
        %p
          = post.description
        %time
          = time_ago_in_words post.published_at
          ago

%section.right
  %section.about
    %p
      Welcome to Macedonian Ruby User Group (MKRUG) - a community of Ruby developers in Macedonia.
    %p
      We meet up at least once a month at #{link_to "Hacklab KIKA", 'http://maps.google.com/maps/ms?ie=UTF8&t=h&hl=en&msa=0&msid=104178503477507895129.00045caee6af59dfd8517&ll=41.988416,21.431478&spn=0.002245,0.003449&z=18', :target => '_blank'} in Skopje - usually every 2nd Thursday.
    %p
      == For next meeting & news #{link_to 'read our blog', posts_path}, for discussions #{link_to 'join our mailing list', 'http://groups.google.com/group/mk-ruby-users-group/', :target => '_blank'}.
